<u>Amateka</u> 

Evelyne Umurerwa n'Umunyarwandakazi wavutse mu mwaka (1977) aho  yavukiye mukarere ka Nyarugenge umugi wa kigali ni mwene  Eduard Nsababera na Blandine Mukasekuru.

<u>Amashuri yize</u>

Evelyne Umurerwa  yize amashuri yisumbuye kukigo cya Centre Islamiques de l'Enseignments  Secondaires de Kigali (CIESK) Akomereza amashuri ya kaminuza  kukigo  cya Kigali independent yiga ishami ryimimibanire.

<u>Akazi yakoze</u>

Umurerwa n'umunyarwandakazi w'umunyamakuru ukorera Radio na television by'Urwanda<ref>https://igihe.com/serivisi/special-pages/womens-month/inkuru/article/urugendo-rwa-umurerwa-evelyne-umaze-imyaka-isaga-17-asoma-amakuru-kuri</ref>  kuva mu mwaka (1998) aho abimazemo imyaka irenga 20,yakoze kuri radio na television by'igihugu agisoza kwiga amashuri yisumbuye .
